{{Navbox/Pride Month}}

[[File:PrideMonth2026 Logo.png|thumb|The banner for Pride Month 2026.]]

The '''Pride Month''' [[Special:MyLanguage/Events|event]] in [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]] is an event annually hosted in the month of June. The event celebrates [[Wikipedia:Pride Month|Pride Month]] while being hosted in a [[VRChat Official Pride Hub|Pride-themed hub world]]. The event also hosts a fundraising campaign called the Pride Campaign, which fundraises for [[Wikipedia:Trans Lifeline|Trans Lifeline]]. Participating users are able to earn several rewards.

== History ==

On May 28, 2025, VRChat posted their plans for a Pride Month event via X and a YouTube video.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1927883086261350413 Celebrate #VRCPride2025 with us this year!]</ref><ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yG6h2G8Di7k Celebrate Pride Month 2025 with Us in #VRChat!]</ref> [[Pride Month 2025]] would start on June 11.<ref>[https://hello.vrchat.com/pride-2025 Celebrate Pride 2025 All Month Long in VRChat]</ref>

On May 29, 2026, VRChat detailed their plans for [[Pride Month 2026]] via X along with an image revealing dates for Pride performances.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/2060400473320858026 We're hosting a party for Pride and we hope you can make it! 💃]></ref> Pride Month 2026 would start on June 1.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/2061539645486477690 HAPPY PRIDE! 🏳️‍🌈]</ref>

== Hub World ==
[[File:VRChat Official Pride Hub world thumbnail.png|thumb|The hub as seen in a thumbnail for [[Pride Month 2025]].]]
{{Main|[[VRChat Official Pride Hub]]}}
Accompanyning the event is a Pride-decorated [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat Home|hub world]]. Users are able to come together to celebrate Pride and the LGBTQIA+ community in this [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]].

It is an island set in the night featuring several Pride decorations: posters and floats as well as flags. You are also able to track the Pride Campaign through campaign boards.

== The Pride Campaign ==
[[File:VRChat Pride Month 2025 event campaign finished screenshot.png|thumb|Menu screenshot of the Pride Campaign finished in 2025.]]

As part of the event, a fundraiser by the name of the Pride Campaign is hosted. The Pride Campaign fundraises for [[Wikipedia:Trans Lifeline|Trans Lifeline]], a trans-led nonprofit and crisis hotline supporting transgender people.<ref>[https://translifeline.org/ Trans Lifelines official website.]</ref> VRChat matches 20% of all [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] gifts and every Gift Drop purchase to Trans Lifeline. You are able to track progress either through the campaign boards in the hubs or through a dedicated tab in the VRC+ page.

During [[Pride Month 2025]], VRChat was able to raise $100,000 for Trans Lifeline by June 20th.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1936086232980676968 We raised $100k to donate to Trans Lifeline!]</ref> Originally, the match for Trans Lifeline was $50,000 but was doubled due to "overwhelming support" only 2 days after the event had started.<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1933634517849321770 VRChat is doubling our match for Trans Lifeline from $50K to $100K!]</ref>

=== Rewards ===

:''See also: [[Pride Month 2025#Rewards]] and [[Pride Month 2026#Rewards]].''

[[File:Accessory Pride Pin.png|60px|thumb|Example of a reward: a Pride pin [[accessory]].]]

Rewards are given to users who participate in the Pride Campaign.

